nodes.text: Hininbirg was an Ton-Falk-class escort carrier used by the Galactic Empire to receive TIE Defender prototypes from cargo ferry group Sela.

It was ambushed by the Rebel Alliance during the transfer from Vinzen Neela 5 to Coruscant, and two CR90 corvettes Vop Hui and Mar Duun attempted to destroy it with a minefield. Fortunately for the Imperials, elite pilot Maarek Stele repulsed the attack and the transfer was a success.
